headline: Open Interest across ICE’s Global Futures and Options Markets Reaches a Record 107 Million Contracts
summary: LONDON & NEW YORK & AMSTERDAM, October 22, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced that its global futures and options markets reached record open interest (OI) of 107.6 million contracts on October 20, 2025, up 16% year-over-year (y/y).
